## Primary Containers
Detail View Panel
A series of data fields laid out in one or more columns

List Panel View
A list of rray objects, or any other data that can be laid out in tabular format

Input set
set of atomic widgets organized in logical groups , must be embedded into detail view panel and hence cannot be directly referenced by secondary containers.

## Secondary containers
Card View:
collection of cards
each card contains detail view or list view

List Detail Panel:
Top view panel- List view
Bottom view panel - details about the selected list item

## Container Widget hierarchy - checkout screenshot 
A List view can contain atomic widget but not Detail view
Atomic widgets can be directly contained only by primary containers
detail view and list view can be contained by screen and secondary containers
Detail view can contain list view


